Title: A Note on Multi-trace Deformations and AdS/CFT

Authors: Amit Sever and Assaf Shomer

Comments: 11 pages, 1 figure, harvmac. v2 typos corrected, version sent to

JHEP. v3 references addedJournal-ref: JHEP 0207 (2002) 027

We derive the general formula, at a finite cutoff, for the change in theboundary condition of a scalar field in AdS under a Multiple-trace deformationof the dual CFT. Our analysis suggests that fluctuations around the classicalsolution in AdS should not be constrained by boundary conditions.